{"type": "article", "id": 15228, "title": "光碟灯罩", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-22T06:38:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003365xHhgOKiMWZNUjlw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t具有雕塑美感的灯泡是 Plumen 系列的标志，英国设计品牌 Hulger 在它上面增加了一个像光碟一样的 Drop Hat ，可以反射出灯泡的形状。它实际是一个灯罩，然而光滑水平的表面和金属的颜色使这款灯增加了一种未来感，同时让悬挂的吊灯保持一种翱翔的姿态。有五种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://usshop.plumen.com/collections/lamp-shades\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142458LMbYiZxpSz2FI1rq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"875\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142459vRJEWDI0yXm37azA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"537\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142459SxOEDqKaIdBY5fbV.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"859\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.43166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}